commit.title: [coqlib] Remove `-boot` option for setting the coqlib
commit.message:
[coqlib] Remove `-boot` option for setting the coqlib

Instead, if the coqlib is special set it explicitly in the command
line, as Dune does.

This is a continuation of #9523.
